reviewText: I am a big James Lee Burke fan and I like Tommy Lee Jones too.  But this is just okay.  Jones' mannerisms are straight from Men in Black, which was distracting.  So much of the book was cut out to make it into a film, that might bother you too if you are a fan of the book.  The General was outstanding in the movie.
I love in the electric mist, but I didn't really like devil's knot
